entries.title: Brexit: Johnson 'very confident' MPs will back deal
entries.content: The PM is facing an uphill battle to get his new Brexit deal through the House of Commons on Saturday.
entries.contentSnippet: The PM is facing an uphill battle to get his new Brexit deal through the House of Commons on Saturday.

entries.title: Turkey to suspend Syria offensive, Mike Pence announces
entries.content: US Vice-President Mike Pence says the pause in operations will allow Kurdish-led forces to withdraw.
entries.contentSnippet: US Vice-President Mike Pence says the pause in operations will allow Kurdish-led forces to withdraw.

entries.title: National Doral Miami: Trump Florida golf course to host G7 summit
entries.content: The Doral Miami resort will host the summit but the president will not profit, the White House says.
entries.contentSnippet: The Doral Miami resort will host the summit but the president will not profit, the White House says.

entries.title: Paul Gascoigne cleared of sex assault on train passenger
entries.content: The ex-footballer has been cleared of both assault and sexual assault after kissing a woman on a train.
entries.contentSnippet: The ex-footballer has been cleared of both assault and sexual assault after kissing a woman on a train.

entries.title: Drayton Manor to be prosecuted over Evha Jannath's death
entries.content: Evha Jannath, 11, died after falling from Drayton Manor's Splash Canyon water ride in 2017.
